
# Platform Audit & Growth Intelligence

Ensuring a clean, production-ready codebase and empowering admins with "Growth Engine" tools to simulate and manage platform activity.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Admin Documentation**: I will create a `ADMIN_PROTCOL.md` in the project root. This file will be marked for **local-only** use and will contain secrets/URLs needed for admin access.
>
> **Growth Engine**: The "Slow Drip" feature will use a cron-like trigger or a background queue (simulated via RPC) to increment metrics over time.
>
> **Dummy Accounts**: These accounts will have generated profiles (DiceBear/Faker-style) but will exist in the `profiles` table with a special `is_dummy` flag.

